comment._content: Yes I think you're right Silupi. This is most likely Grinna lighthouse.There has been some additions to the lighthouse during the years, but have a look at this recent image in comparison with the old one: picasaweb.google.com/steinfjorden/FollaKystlag#5338554021.... The image also has similarities with Lille Presteskjær, but there is something with the shape of the lighthouse and the location of the windows that doesn't quite add up, in my view.
